    "prompt": "A detailed technical architecture diagram illustrating a multimodal human-computer interaction system. The diagram shows a closed-loop model labeled 'Perception-Intent-Feedback', with arrows connecting hardware sensor arrays, edge computing modules, and cloud collaboration. It includes icons for EMG sensors, bend sensors, IMUs, and a communication protocol layer labeled 'Lightweight Protocol' connecting to icons of PICO and Unity China XR platforms. The background has a clean, futuristic tech aesthetic.",
    "alt": "多模态交互系统“感知-意图-反馈”闭环技术框架图"
  }
}

